probably wildebeest, in the background. BILL ABBOTT; Map, Camping in Kenya, Los 
Angeles Times ; Photo, COLOR, The accommodations may be simple, but camping out 
in Kenya's Amboseli National Park allows visitors unforgettable views of Mt. 
Kilimanjaro in neighboring Tanzania, top.; Photo, COLOR, Campers also 
experience the romance and reality of Africa by getting eyeball to eyeball with 
elephants, hippos and lions in Kenya's vast wildlife parks. MITCH REARDON / 
TSW; Photo, COLOR, Hippo NICHOLA PARFITT /TSW; Photo, COLOR, Elephant MARGARET 
COWMAN /TSW 
</P>
